				"description":{
					"value":"<p class=\"flavour\"><i>Bridges of golden magic force blink on and off, connecting and disconnecting the floating platforms to and from one another.</i></p><p><b>Trap:</b> When the beholder reveals itself, the bridges start to cycle through their off-active-push-active cycle.</p>",
